{"tid":1666780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳健波：香港已被民主派「搞到亂晒龍」 我不會向惡勢力低頭","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T10:46:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08d7fa008b99f2327c234507806562e43a3d8094","tid":1666780,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"立法會財委會上午開會選舉副主席，24名民主派議員挑戰建制派唯一候選人金融界的陳振英。<br />\n<br />\n多名參選議員輪流發表政綱及質詢，但未能開始總結發言，主席陳健波原本提出加時15分鐘，受到民主派反對，最後會議在原定的時間結束。<br />\n<br />\n另外，議員郭家麒批評陳健波處理撥款申請時「皇帝唔急太監急」，<span style=\"color: red;\">陳健波說對方的說話毋須理會，因為沒有人會相信</span>，之後引起民主派不滿。陳健波收回言論，仍未能平息爭議，民主派要求他道歉，陳健波拒絕，說不覺得自己要道歉，<span style=\"color: red;\">又指香港已被民主派「搞到亂晒龍」，強調他不會向惡勢力低頭</span>。他說，參選副主席的陳振英「靚仔」、好人、有智慧，如果他當選，日後會讓他有多些機會主持會議，民主派就達到目的。<br />\n<br />\n民主派質疑陳健波的講法有拉票之嫌，他之後再次收回言論。最終會議召開兩個小時仍未選出副主席，需要在今個星期五的會議繼續。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487389-20191021.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487389-20191021.htm&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERbtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=e74d2400\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487389-20191021.htm&h=1953606b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487389-20191021.htm</a>"},{"pid":"247debda80b672b599a713411f8824de6271302d","tid":1666780,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:29:10.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8131bfc8fb9c175e2029801970f9802d4d3be0","tid":1666780,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"「靚仔」、好人???? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce54437e64b7f576c1b91c138a126a89f4f75a39","tid":1666780,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾真係好撚垃圾"},{"pid":"3f5abd148244d07c3e232e380526d89fbc7b79d2","tid":1666780,"uid":293227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"冇人care 你低唔低頭"},{"pid":"1aac9b559f46cbe4c6233ce0825657d3b7d5389f","tid":1666780,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:33:41.000Z","msg":"呢個收成期一定要入人權法名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔俾佢有得收成"},{"pid":"f1c4f33649b9c188319ddbb287e822760eee68d1","tid":1666780,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"陳健波住邊?"},{"pid":"b42a6c87e72a91dbf4eaf68b18457eeffbed5171","tid":1666780,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:46:57.000Z","msg":"佢咩國籍？"}]}